The paper discusses improvement and extension approaches for composite (modular) systems, which involves the evaluation and optimization of system components and their interconnections. This topic falls under the scope of software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of various optimization problems and heuristics, which are common in computer science (cs.DS) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the modification of system structure, which can be related to programming languages and compilers (cs.PL).
